N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 274.7 - First stage resolution

State Regulations

Within 90 days of issuance of the notice of approved
complaint, commissioner's staff will review the information submitted and
will: (a) recommend a resolution; or
(b) upon stipulation of the
parties and withdrawal of the complaint, discontinue the investigation; or
(c) specify additional
information, if any, to be submitted, schedule a meeting, or schedule a
hearing. Notes
